<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Player Not Found</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nanum+Brush+Script&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"> <!-- 나눔손글씨 붓 폰트 추가 -->
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Nanum Brush Script', cursive; /* 나눔손글씨 붓으로 폰트 변경 */
            background-color: #FFC0CB; /* 연분홍색 배경 */
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #E91E63; /* 진한 핑크색 */
            font-size: 28px;
        }

        p {
            color: #444; /* 더 어둡게 */
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        form {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        input[type="hidden"] {
            display: none;
        }

        button {
            background-color: #FF69B4;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 18px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        button:hover {
            background-color: #FFB6C1;
        }

        .message {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #E91E63;
            margin-top: 10px;
            display: inline-block;
            vertical-align: top;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>😢 플레이어를 찾을 수 없습니다!</h1>
    <p><%= playerName %>의 통계를 찾을 수 없어요.</p>
    <form action="/soccer/updatePlayerStats" method="post" style="display: inline-block;">
        <input type="hidden" name="playerName" value="<%= playerName %>" />
        <input type="hidden" name="leagueId" value="<%= leagueId %>" />
        <input type="hidden" name="existence" value="<%= existence %>" />
        <button type="submit">딸깍</button>
    </form>
    <span class="message">뿌우 딸깍 딸깍! 얼마나 쉬워요??</span>
</body>
